contentrichtext.text: '''KHJ''' may refer to: * [[KHJ (AM)]], a radio station (930 AM) licensed to Los Angeles, California, United States * [[KRTH]], a radio station (101.1 FM) licensed to Los Angeles, California, United States, which formerly used the call sign KHJ-FM * [[KCAL-TV]], a television station (channel 9 analog/43 digital) licensed to Los Angeles, California, United States, which used the call sign KHJ-TV from December 1958 to December 1989 * [[KKHJ-FM]], a radio station (93.1 FM) licensed to Pago Pago, American Samoa, which uses the branding ''93 KHJ'' * [[KKHJ-LP]], a low-power television station (channel 30) licensed to Pago Pago, American Samoa, which uses the branding ''KHJ-TV'' * [[CKHJ (AM)]], a radio station (1260 AM) licensed to Fredericton, New Brunswick, Canada, which uses the branding ''KHJ'' * [[WKHJ]], a radio station (104.5 FM) licensed to Mountain Lake Park, Maryland, which uses the branding ''KHJ'' * The IATA airport code for [[Kauhajoki Airport]] in Finland {{disambig|callsign|airport}} {{DEFAULTSORT:Khj}}
